Text:
For fragment to have a shot at receiving callback for **onActivityResult**, your **activity** must implement `onActivityResult()` and should have a call to `super` too.

For further explanations you can also see [this][1] answer.


  [1]: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/6147884/onactivityresult-is-not-being-called-in-fragment
